<section>
	<h1>About truckload.io</h1>
	<p>
		<strong>truckload.io</strong> is a browser-based 3D visualization and optimization tool for truckload packing.
		It helps you figure out exactly how freight fits into a trailer before it ever touches a dock.
	</p>
	<p>
		Whether you're planning a single shipment or optimizing recurring loads, truckload.io gives you a visual,
		interactive way to arrange cargo, identify dead space, and export a finalized packing plan — all without
		leaving your browser.
	</p>
</section>

<section>
	<h2>Features</h2>
	<ul>
		<li>Interactive 3D visualization of trailer space</li>
		<li>Load optimization to minimize wasted space</li>
		<li>Browser-based — no installation required</li>
		<li>Exportable packing plans</li>
	</ul>
</section>

